About Us

Not just coffee —
a space for you.

Near Coffee was born from a simple belief: everyone deserves a place nearby where they can slow down. Whether you're closing a deal, writing your first chapter, or simply watching the world go by — we built this for you.

01 Comfort Spaces designed to feel like a second home.
02 Quality Carefully sourced, expertly crafted coffee.
03 Community Where connections happen naturally.
Our Spaces

Every space,
a different feeling.

Each Near Coffee location has its own identity — crafted to match the energy of the neighborhood it lives in.

01

The Workshop

Bright, open, productive. Designed for deep-focus work and casual brainstorming alike. Grab a read, grab a coffee, and get into the flow.

02

The Garden

Soft light, green textures, and a calm that invites you to stay a little longer. Fresh pastries, good coffee, better company.

03

The Lounge

Warm evenings, good conversations, and coffee that makes you forget the clock. The kind of place you don't want to leave.

Our Vision

Building a network of spaces people love.

Near Coffee is more than one location — it's a growing family of unique cafes, each with its own personality, united by one shared philosophy: great coffee in a space that feels like it was built just for you.
